(593, 1, '2019-12-07 23:34:15', '2019-12-07 16:34:15', '[page_header height=\"300px\" style=\"simple\" align=\"center\" title_case=\"uppercase\" bg=\"318\"]\n\n[section]\n\n[gap height=\"40px\"]\n\n[row h_align=\"center\"]\n\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"10\"]\n\n<h1 class=\"custom-font\"><span style=\"font-size: 160%;\">Chnh sch bo hnh</span></h1>\n[button text=\"get in touch with us\" style=\"link\" icon=\"icon-angle-right\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"8\" span__sm=\"10\"]\n\n<p>Mi sn phm n tay qu khch hng u l nhng sn phm  c Lak kim tra mc  hon thin cao nht. Nhng trong qu trnh s dng, chc chn khng th trnh khi nhng h hng hoc b oxi ho en. V vy, Juz Style s:</p>\n<p>Bo hnh nh sng min ph v thi hn i vi sn phm bc nguyn cht 92.5% khng m Rhodium (hoc vng hng, vng 14K, vng 18K, vng 24K).</p>\n<p>Bo hnh nc m cho cc sn phm bc nguyn cht 92.5% m Rhodium, vng hng v vng 14K, 18K, 24K trong vng 1 thng. Qua thi gian bo hnh, ph m li l 20.000/ ln/ sn phm.</p>\n<p>Bo hnh kho, mc sn phm trong vng 3 thng i vi tt c sn phm. Qu thi hn bo hnh, ph thay kho, mc l 20.000/ ln/ sn phm.</p>\n<p>Khng bo hnh t, gy dy v nhn, ph sa cha t 20.000 - 40.000/ ln/ sn phm. i vi dy chuyn b t gia dy khng sa c, nu qu khch mun, Lak s thay li dy mi vi mc ph t 70.000 - 100.000/ ln/ sn phm.</p>\n<p>Khng bo hnh ht nh trn sn phm, nu sn phm b ri ht hoc b mt ht, ph gn li bao gm ht mi l 20.000/ ht v khi mt nhiu ht th Lak s cn nhc mc ph thp nht c th.</p>\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]', 'Chnh sch bo hnh', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'chinh-sach-bao-hanh', '', '', '2019-12-07 23:36:45', '2019-12-07 16:36:45', '', 0, 'http://localhost/lak/?page_id=593', 0, 'page', '', 0),
