(604, 1, '2019-12-07 23:32:58', '2019-12-07 16:32:58', '[page_header height=\"300px\" style=\"simple\" align=\"center\" title=\"Gii thiu\" title_case=\"uppercase\" bg=\"318\"]\n\n[section]\n\n[gap height=\"40px\"]\n\n[row h_align=\"center\"]\n\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"10\"]\n\n<h1 class=\"custom-font\"><span style=\"font-size: 200%;\">Chnh sch bo mt</span></h1>\n[button text=\"get in touch with us\" style=\"link\" icon=\"icon-angle-right\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"8\" span__sm=\"10\"]\n\n<p>Khi truy cp vo website ca Lak ngha l qu khch ng  v chp nhn thc hin nhng m t trong Chnh sch bo mt thng tin. Nu qu khch khng ng  vi cc iu khon ca Chnh sch bo mt thng tin, vui lng khng s dng website ca Lak. Chnh sch bo mt ny c a ra  th hin vai tr ca Lak trong vn  bo mt trc tuyn v dch v khch hng.</p>\n<p><strong>1. Mc ch v phm vi thu thp thng tin:</strong></p>\n<p>Vic thu thp thng tin qua websiteLaks gip chng ti:</p>\n<p>- Nhn n hng trc tuyn t khch hng v thc hin cc bc lin h xc nhn v giao hng n a ch ca khch hng;</p>\n<p>- Gip khch hng cp nht nhng sn phm mi nht ca Lak hoc cc chng trnh khuyn mi, gim gi khc ca Lak. ng thi, Lak c th h tr nhanh nht khi c khiu ni t pha khch hng.</p>\n<p>Thng tin khch hng Lak thu thp gm:</p>\n<p> - H tn</p>\n<p> - Email</p>\n<p> - in thoi</p>\n<p> - a ch</p>\n<p> - Ngy thng nm sinh</p>\n<p> - Gii tnh</p>\n<p><strong>2. Phm vi s dng thng tin:</strong></p>\n<p>Lak rt coi trng vic bo mt thng tin khch hng nn chng ti cam kt s tuyt i gi b mt thng tin khch hng, khng t  s dng thng tin khch hng vi mc ch khng mang li li ch cho khch hng. Chng ti cam kt khng bun bn, trao i thng tin bo mt ca khch hng cho bt k bn th ba no. Lak ch s dng thng tin ca khch hng  lu tr thng tin khch hng thn thit, u i dnh ring cho khch hng.</p>\n<p><strong>3. Thi gian lu tr thng tin:</strong></p>\n<p>Lak s lu tr cc thng tin c nhn do khch hng cung cp trn h thng ni b ca chng ti trong qu trnh cung cp dch v cho khch hng hoc cho n khi hon thnh mc ch thu thp thng tin hoc khi khch hng c yu cu hy cc thng tin  cung cp.</p>\n<p><strong>4. a ch ca n v thu thp v qun l thng tin c nhn:</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Email:</strong>lak@gmail.com</p>\n<p><strong>Phone:</strong>+ 84 0902672322</p>\n<p><strong>a ch:</strong>Qun 2, TP. H Ch Minh. Thanh kh,  Nng.</p>\n<p><strong>5. Phng tin v cng c  ngi dng tip cn v chnh sa d liu c nhn ca mnh.</strong></p>\n<p>Khch hng c th thc hin cc quyn tip cn v chnh sa d liu c nhn bng cch truy cp vo website hoc lin h vi chng ti qua email hoc a ch lin lc c cng b trn website lak.com,vn</p>\n<p><strong>6. Cam kt bo mt thng tin c nhn khch hng:</strong></p>\n<p>Chng ti cam kt m bo an ton thng tin cho qu khch hng khi ng k thng tin c nhn trn website ca Lak. Lak cam kt khng trao i mua bn thng tin khch hng.</p>\n<p> m bo thng tin ca khch hng c bo mt tt nht, chng ti khuyn co khch hng nn s dng mt khu c  phc tp cao, khng ng nhp ti khon ca mnh ti cc dch v my tnh cng cng, thng xuyn qut virus trn my tnh ca qu khch. Chng ti s khng chu trch nhim khi nhng thng tin c nhn ca qu khch b r r v nhng nguyn nhn t pha khch hng.</p>\n<p>Chnh sch bo mt ch p dng khi khch hng ng k trn website chnh thc ca Lak. Mi thng tin qu khch hng ng k ti nhng website khc u khng thuc phm vi hiu lc ca chnh sch bo mt thng tin ny.</p>\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]', 'Chnh sch bo mt', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '592-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-12-07 23:32:58', '2019-12-07 16:32:58', '', 592, 'http://localhost/lak/592-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
