(654, 1, '2019-12-08 01:00:03', '2019-12-07 18:00:03', '[page_header height=\"300px\" style=\"simple\" align=\"center\" title_case=\"uppercase\" bg=\"318\"]\n\n[section]\n\n[gap height=\"40px\"]\n\n[row h_align=\"center\"]\n\n[col span=\"4\" span__sm=\"10\"]\n\n<h1  class=\"custom-font\"><span style=\"font-size: 200%;\">V chng ti</span></h1><h1></p>\n[button text=\"get in touch with us\" style=\"link\" icon=\"icon-angle-right\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"8\" span__sm=\"10\"]\n\n<p>Nm 2011, khi trang sc bc thi trang vn cn l mt khi nhim mi m vi cc bn tr Vit, Juz Style c sinh ra trn mt cn gc nh nm trong con hm khng tn gia Si Gn. Ngi sng lp Juz Style tin rng, trang sc khng dng li  thi trang m n cn mang  ngha v du n quan trng ca ch nhn. V  cng l khi u ca hnh trnh sng to Juz Style n tn by gi.</p>\n<p>Mi mt mn trang sc Juz Style to ra u c truyn cm hng t nhng cu chuyn v tnh yu, tnh bn, tnh cm gia nh, nhng cm xc vui v, nhng ct mc ng nh Nu l ngi yu phong cch sng n gin, hin i, tinh t v tr trung ca ngi Nht, chc hn bn s tm thy nim si m  tng mn trang sc d nh nht ca Juz Style.</p>\n<p>c xy dng t tnh yu v s t t vi trang sc, sn phm ca Juz Style l s kt tinh ca hng gi t m ch tc th cng ca ngi th bc Vit Nam. Juz Style mong rng s mang n cho bn nhng mn qu  ngha nht khng ch  lm p cho bn thn m cn lm p cho tm hn.Cm n bn  dnh thi gian  hiu v Juz Style.</p>\n<p>Mi bn tip tc khm ph Juz Style thng qua nhng sng to mi nht ca Juz Style ti y.</p>\n<p>Lak - Just be your style.</p>\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]', 'Chnh sch bo mt', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '592-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-12-08 01:00:03', '2019-12-07 18:00:03', '', 592, 'http://localhost/lak/592-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
